title: [CF&B] Detective Conan 001-123 (BATCH) [ENG-SUB]
description:
My description from nyaa (user sarachikorita):

Since starting this project I've reissued some episodes silently in later torrents, so here's a full list of changes/new eps over previous batches:

V2: 17, 34, 43, 64, 96, 111, 119

New to this batch: 120, 121, 122, 123

This release completes the CF&B Detective Conan project.  Baaro will continue to work on selected episodes with periodic new releases, although for some episodes a translator who does not need to rely on captions would be quite helpful.  (Contact Licca in #fusion-rips on irc.hoshinet.org.)

Additional text:

This is R2J with occasional grafts from R1 (mainly in episodes 7, 8 and 10), with edited R1 subtitles.  To save work, the English dub is NOT included, only Japanese audio with English subtitles.  These MKVs are 100% softsub.
